Sentencas: A novel Ir0.5Mn0.5O2 cathode has been synthesized by thermal decomposition of mixed H2IrCl6 and Mn(NO3)(2) water solution.
Titulo: Evaluation of nano-structured Ir0.5Mn0.5O2 as a potential cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The Ir0.5Mn0.5O2 cathode has been characterized by XRD, field emission SEM (FESEM) and AC impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Evaluation of nano-structured Ir0.5Mn0.5O2 as a potential cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: XRD result shows that rutile-structured Ir0.5Mn0.5O2 phase is formed by thermal decomposition of mixed H2IrCl6 and Mn(NO3)(2) water solution.
Titulo: Evaluation of nano-structured Ir0.5Mn0.5O2 as a potential cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: FESEM micrographs show that a porous structure with well-necked particles forms in the cathode after sintering at 1000 degrees C.
Titulo: Evaluation of nano-structured Ir0.5Mn0.5O2 as a potential cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The average grain size is between 20 and 30 nm.
Titulo: Evaluation of nano-structured Ir0.5Mn0.5O2 as a potential cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Two depressed arcs appear in the medium-frequency and low-frequency region, indicating that there are at least two different processes in the cathode reaction: charge transfer and molecular oxygen dissociation followed by surface diffusion.
Titulo: Evaluation of nano-structured Ir0.5Mn0.5O2 as a potential cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The minimum area specific resistance (ASR) is 0.67 Omega cm(2) at 800 degrees
Titulo: Evaluation of nano-structured Ir0.5Mn0.5O2 as a potential cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The activation energy for the total oxygen reduction reaction is 93.7 kJ mol(-1).
